Class ProxyServerSocket

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.net.ServerSocket
      • edu.umass.cs.msocket.proxy.forwarder.ProxyServerSocket
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable

    public class ProxyServerSocket
extends ServerSocket
    This class is for accepting connections at the proxy, It implements the proxy's listening server socket. It accepts the connection from both servers and clients.
